" Help — status keys ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────"
"Actions                                                                                                                 "
" j  move down                           <c-k>  command palette                                                          "
" k  move up                             ?  help                                                                         "
" gg  go to top                          q  back                                                                         "
" G  go to bottom                        c  Commit …                                                                     "
" <c-d>  half page down                    c  Commit                                                                     "
" <c-u>  half page up                      e  Extend                                                                     "
" v  mark the file viewed                  a  Amend                                                                      "
" <c-n>  next section                      w  Reword                                                                     "
" <c-p>  previous section                b  Branch …                                                                     "
" <tab>  fold / unfold                     b  Checkout branch                                                            "
" s  stage file or hunk                    c  Create and checkout                                                        "
" u  unstage file or hunk                  n  Create                                                                     "
" S  stage everything                      D  Delete                                                                     "
" U  unstage everything                    p  Pull requests                                                              "
" x  discard changes                     l  Log …                                                                        "
" <c-r>  refresh                           l  Current branch                                                             "
" <cr>  open the item under the cursor   P  Push …                                                                       "
" D  open the full working-tree diff       p  Push                                                                       "
" o  open CI runs                          u  Push and set upstream                                                      "
" {  previous hunk                       p  Pull …                                                                       "
" }  next hunk                             p  Pull                                                                       "
" e  open in $EDITOR                     f  Fetch …                                                                      "
" Z  send feedback to waiting agents       f  Fetch                                                                      "
" C  overview of every comment             a  Fetch all remotes                                                          "
" /  search                              z  Stash …                                                                      "
" n  next search match                     z  Stash changes                                                              "
" N  previous search match                 p  Pop latest stash                                                           "
